                    <h1 class='article-title '>â¬ÜOur combined effort can help move people from poverty to possibilityâ¬"</h1>
                    	<div class="subtitle">Five Concordians explain what supporting Centraide means for them</div>

                    <div class="clearfix"></div>

                    <div class="infos">
                        <div class="row-fluid stack-tablet-1 stack-mobile-1">
